---
title: HelloHero: Spiced Chicken & Currant Couscous with Yoghurt & Almonds
description: Couscous - the grain so nice they named it twice! Here we’ve added sweet currants and nutty almonds for a pop of flavour and topped the whole thing off with mildly spiced chicken strips and greens. Don’t forget a generous dollop of cooling yoghurt to bring the meal together.
